comments: Green (GSW) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Ibaka (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Green (GSW).
Cousins (GSW) is in the paint and actively guarding an opponent within three seconds.
Cousins (GSW) makes contact to the body of Siakam (TOR) during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) releases from the contact with VanVleet (TOR) prior to moving around the screen.
Cousins (GSW) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of VanVleet (TOR) and does not deliver contact.
Lowry (TOR) imminently actively guarding an opponent within three seconds.
LAR shows Lowry (TOR) is late to the spot and continues to move into Cousins (GSW), grabbing his arm and affecting his movement to the basket.
Ibaka (TOR) firms up in a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to Iguodala (GSW).
LLS shows Iguodala (GSW) makes incidental contact with Leonard's (TOR) hand after the shot has been released that does not affect Leonard's jump shot attempt.
While Curry (GSW) is stationary, Lowry (TOR) briefly grasps his arm but the contact does not affect his FOM.
As Curry (GSW) begins to move around the screen, he and VanVleet (TOR) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Leonard (TOR) maintains legal guarding position as he absorbs the contact from Curry (GSW) and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Leonard (TOR) knocks the ball into the backcourt, where Green (GSW) legally retrieves it.
Siakam  (TOR) and Livingston (GSW) briefly engage and disengage in the post.
Siakam (TOR) legally contests the driving shot attempt by Cousins (GSW), as he jumps alongside of Cousins and makes incidental contact with his arm following the release of the shot.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Siakam (TOR) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of VanVleet (TOR) and does not deliver contact.
RLB shows Siakam (TOR) moves into Curry (GSW) and makes contact with his left leg/foot, causing him to trip and affecting his SQBR.
Green (TOR) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Iguodala (GSW) and does not deliver contact.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Green (TOR) that does not affect his ability to make the pass.  Any contact to Green's arms after the pass is released is deemed incidental.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Green (TOR) throws the ball to Siakam (TOR), who is the last player to touch it before it goes out of bounds.
VanVleet (TOR) briefly places two hands on Curry (GSW) but does not affect his FOM during the inbound.
As the pass is thrown, Green (GSW) has his hands rested on Siakam's (TOR) back and he releases from the contact as he attempts to retrieve the pass.
Ibaka (TOR) briefly grasps Cousins' (GSW) jersey and releases it away from the play.
Cousins (GSW) firms up his screening position and does not deliver contact to VanVleet (TOR).
VanVleet (TOR) makes incidental contact with Curry (GSW) that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Cousins (GSW) and Leonard (TOR) make incidental contact with each other during the loose ball.
Leonard (TOR) dives for the loose ball and any contact with Green (GSW) is incidental.
Multiple players on the Warriors signal for a timeout with no timeouts remaining.  Due to the excessive timeout, the Warriors are correctly assessed a technical foul and loss of possession.
Iguodala (GSW) grabs Leonard's (TOR) arm.  After communicating with the Replay Center, it is confirmed that the foul occurred after the ball is inbounded.
